        </p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3569"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Siegler: der <rs type="person" ref="pe__ulrich_eitzinger_QGW_II_II_3270">Aussteller</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="pe__georg_dachsner_QGW_II_II_3487">der <roleName type="title">edel</roleName>
